title: Confirmation before clearing all students
body: Pop-up when "clear students" button is clicked. If click "Ok", clears students. If "Cancel", nothing happens.

title: Improved Layout and Submission for Student Issue Form
body: Refactored the student issue form to use Bootstrap for its layout. Additionally, streamlined the form submission process by using more standard idioms for form validation and submission. One important caveat to note: I was unable to add anyone to the queue when running the site locally. I am fairly sure that I did not introduce this issue, but we still should get to the bottom of that before merging this pull request.

title: Improved Security for TA Password
body: These changes make the process of authenticating TAs (somewhat) more secure. Essentially, it hashes the inputted password using SHA256 and compares it to a precomputed hash of the actual password. This means that the password is no longer stored in plaintext in the source code of the website, responding to multiple people's complaints during Friday's staff meeting. Now, in order for someone to crack the password, they would need to reverse the precomputed SHA256 hash (which is quite a task). That being said, other security flaws still exist in the process that should probably be addressed before launch.
